  • Enum Constant Details

    • EQUIVALENCE

      public static final CorrespondenceRelation EQUIVALENCE
      Equivalence relation, when two concepts are exactly the same (has the same intension/semantic). Represents an OWL equivalence relation.

    • SUBSUME

      public static final CorrespondenceRelation SUBSUME
      Represents a subsumption relation. Entity one (source/left) is "greater" than entity two (target/right).

    • SUBSUMED

      public static final CorrespondenceRelation SUBSUMED
      Represents a subsumption relation. Entity one (source/left) is "smaller" than entity two (target/right).

    • NON_TRANSITIVE_IMPLICATION

      public static final CorrespondenceRelation NON_TRANSITIVE_IMPLICATION
      Non transitive implication relation (see work of C-OWL and others).

    • INSTANCE_OF

      public static final CorrespondenceRelation INSTANCE_OF
      The relation between an instance and class. Entity one (source/left) is the instance than entity two (target/right) is the class.

    • HAS_INSTANCE

      public static final CorrespondenceRelation HAS_INSTANCE
      Has instance relation which connects a class (source/left) to its instances (target/right)

    • INCOMPAT

      public static final CorrespondenceRelation INCOMPAT
      Incompatiple relation mening that two concepts should not be matched.

    • UNKNOWN
